### Steps to reproduce

This test is failing in the release automation:
`FileSystem.Tests.ps1`    ->     `Remove-Item UnAuthorized Access`

The test has a 10 second delay which suggests fragility.

### Expected behavior

```console
Expect test to run and succeed on all Windows platforms
```


### Actual behavior

```console
Test fails on Win11 SKU
```
